{"tid":1542374,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緊急 - 向法庭申請CCTV","createTime":"2019-09-04T23:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T11:07:25.000Z","uid":71037,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"922bce87589c190a00c4ccf6325ad44d13130786","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RzW0krg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzW0krg.jpg&h=5e85e4a3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"296417beb74251b0906e6b9d190358a474bb01c3","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:50:19.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid":"b196b34c1f682073c580c889c9365bb373c9aea7","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:50:31.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid":"d79887777656fe5dec4436b5f92a1ea7403b7103","tid":1542374,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3814ee3e8b4be3cda003cc7b8fc437e5e2d7490","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:50:41.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid":"2691c61cd9c0b25f5615d39b914501354a4d4a74","tid":1542374,"uid":59873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:50:45.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"bd3cb81e2ac1ea15ce8671483d8e48a895241c2e","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:50:52.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid":"89c373066f47158f3098ca03a44fe08994ce632e","tid":1542374,"uid":6197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:50:56.000Z","msg":"(手動轉戴)<br />\n<br />\n最快兩日，黨鐵就可以刪除831晚太子站cctv，到時你、被防暴圍毆嘅抗爭者同乘客，唔會再攞得返公道。<br />\n<br />\n之前講過無論你係受傷定受驚，都可以向香港警察或港鐵提出民事訴訟，申請要法庭強制命令黨鐵交出831當晚既CCTV。 有法庭命令，黨鐵唔交就係藐視法庭！😡<br />\n<br />\n成班義務律師大狀已經準備就緒，但到而家仲未有任何831受害人contact 義務律師！🤯😔<br />\n其實受害人唔使怕有咩隱憂，例如自爆、金錢、時間，義務律師會同你傾咗先，商量吓再決定告唔告，一切內容絕對保密。🤐👌<br />\n<br />\n港鐵每7-28日就會清一次cctv，換言之我哋最快得返兩日去揾證據，時間一過，在場所有人受到嘅傷害、屈辱，將會永遠石沉大海，而毆打你哋嘅武裝分子繼續逍遙法外，無後果地打壓香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n就喺呢兩日，你可以選擇還831傷者一個公道，將黑警暴行昭告天下。就算你唔喺現場，都請你幫手推post，比在場者見到為止。<br />\n<br />\n831受害者請盡快聯絡以下團體：<br />\n<br />\n1. 星火: 9819 0979 <br />\n2. 民陣:6549 9452 <br />\n3. 民權: 9463 2945 <br />\n4. 伍展邦:2608 1400<br />\n<br />\n(白影: 4係我相熟既朋友都用開既律師)"},{"pid":"2bbbceabd1605439b9fea1cbb1c8df91f13ec0a0","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:51:03.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid":"912868339e258c642761eb3b6858efec695be447","tid":1542374,"uid":84982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:51:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09ad7f6f42c491df8361d365dbb8c630b492fcf4","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:51:13.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid":"1263b63a041f2f8c44c25dd178d744b85330b344","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:51:23.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid":"6162c53f082913f4b9b7dd48c0f323d5b99d24a1","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:51:33.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid":"ef59a7c5916a515d0c76433faa2a73cdec73a5b5","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:51:44.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid":"f6e911190fb44f52928a4d642b5589a2e7a93e11","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:51:56.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid":"4f3a0facd0be1a961270c685269f882b999b0a14","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:52:08.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid":"8a018f7fc860564359f10ae2420a8ec1afffdb4c","tid":1542374,"uid":71037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:52:18.000Z","msg":"自推10 連"},{"pid"